node.content: ["NEW YORK - Former New York City police union president Ed Mullins surrendered to federal authorities Wednesday.\u00a0", "Mullins\u00a0served as president of the Sergeants Benevolent Association.\u00a0 \u00a0", "His surrender comes five months after the FBI raided his home and office.\u00a0", "Federal officials say the raid was connected to allegations of misappropriation of union funds.\u00a0", "The CBSNewYork team is a group of experienced journalists who bring you the content on CBSNewYork.com."]
